nessus-libraries (0.99.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version.
  * Actually *link* libnessus0.so to system libpcap (doh!).
  * Made "-O2 -Wall -D_REENTRANT" the compiler flags, and fixed some
    stuff to make it propagate $CFLAGS to all subdirectories.
