    libraries, but to link dynamically with those from libgmp2 and zlib1g
    packages, partly using Gorgo's patch. Closes: #49407.
  * Removed extra {pcap,zlib}.3 manual pages. Closes: #49466.
  * Minor adjustments in debian/*.

